title: Worst Date Wednesday: He Packed an Overnight Bag
description: Sarah tells us the story of her first date with someone from Tinder that came to her place and brought an overnight bag with him.  He then proceeded to pull out a huge burrito and eat it.  It gets funnier, and a little weird as the date goes on...
